                    <font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="3"><br>
                      <b>Blonde<br>
                      </b>A blonde gets a call from a bill collector:<br>
                      <br>
                      "We have been waiting for payment for your new
                      windows for over a year. When can we expect to get
                      paid?".<br>
                      <br>
                      The blonde replies:<br>
                      <br>
                      "How stupid do you think I am? When the salesman
                      sold me the windows he told me they would pay for
                      themselves within a year."<br>
                      <br>
